{"type": "article", "id": 35394, "title": "让自行车站在墙上，又多了一种方法｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-08T23:06:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 809, "name": "Vitra"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 123, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161209064133YL8jMaXAZGB9OyU2.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Light Dusk by Z-Inhouse</h3><p>宛如陶罐的铝制灯罩搭配质朴的软木，造作旗下的设计师利用两种材质的特性，打造了这个造型简洁的向晚小吊灯。喇叭形的灯罩由 1.5 毫米厚的轻薄铝板制成，表面还经过了哑光喷涂处理。嵌入顶部的软木塞则为吊灯添加了一丝温暖的感觉，可以更好地融入各种居家环境当中。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300174\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 285 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081702367dCyT8MHXGVSFU1f.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461458\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170236T9rG7IykXJc6RPh0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081702360GcNAioOwvUjTQk9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081702366BgL7QeUqY0IC9Si.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Allstar chair by Konstantin Grcic</h3><p>在线设计杂志 Dezeen 最近新增一间位于运河边的东伦敦办公室，并选择了德国设计师 <a href=\"http://konstantin-grcic.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Konstantin Brcic</a> 为 Vitra 设计的 Allstar 作为办公椅。这张没有传统椅背的办公椅有着简单又很讨巧的构造：一根弯曲的塑料管将靠垫和座位收在其中，既起到了固定的作用，又能作为椅子的扶手。除了底座和座位之外，塑料管和靠垫的颜色都可以定制。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170328MBq4EGY5WJ2z7ftX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565990\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170328QkNKcS3qUysgMiLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170328bK2jhrH17SfE0W3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081703281cmOqIdzRLh740QV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PARKIS</h3><p>将自行车以垂直的方式收纳起来并不是什么全新的概念，但对力气比较小或是行动不便的用户来说，操作起来还是不够省力。最近一个来自比利时的设计团队带来了这款名为 PARKIS 的自行车竖放装置，只要将前轮对准卡位器，顺势向前一推，自行车就会沿着轨道自动升起，卡位器最后会固定在卡槽上，让自行车保持稳定的垂直状态。归功于这一构造，卸下时也只要轻轻一拉即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/277601164/parkis-space-saving-bicycle-lift\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 239 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170257DVykMgqwGE5vtcJ6.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081702525d1FlvbUZchTCwRP.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170251s4FMZ6kYw3gCVfT9.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.019146\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170252xIZ8B2Xrw7YSeHMb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.014706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170253z9RFY6okC1JWSpwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Everlast Notebook by Rocket Innovations</h3><p><a href=\"http://getrocketbook.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rocket Innovations</a> 是一个来自美国波士顿的团队，专注于智能、环保的笔记本研发。最近他们又推出了一款名为 Everlast 的笔记本，打的同样是再利用的招牌：笔记本的内页由聚酯合成纤维制成，如果使用百乐（Pilot）的 Frixion 中性笔在上面写字，用湿布可以将字迹擦拭掉，从而起到重复使用的效果。Everlast 有一个配套的应用，对准页面拍照时会识别笔记内容并储存为图片形式。除此之外，内页底部还标有 7 种云端服务的 logo，只要你提前在上面做好标记，应用也会将它们识别出来并自动传送到指定的云端。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/642311833/everlast\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 34 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208175036PrOXs2beGNF4aQpZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208175034ofNtG63YjnqLyDhW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208175035EYmIaViQ6GNg5fye.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.264706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208175034GNYTo78ndgU1Bbmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.901471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Iris walker by Reut Meiri</h3><p>虽然现在还无法彻底回避衰老带来的诸多不便，但助行器的设计似乎总是无法摆脱沉重、老土的标签。设计师 Reut Meiri 为此带来了这款名为 Iris 的概念助行器，纤细轻质的支架加上配套的小包使它在使用上更为灵活，造型也优雅了不少。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208180839JGazqcQpRdV4Wti5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208180839g8eRPTFW7paXZtEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208180839XSEokshP2f01Tmx7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081808402ZdvWY05TBRni9Al.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208180840YT2OnaAiyRtkoQcD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.508571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Delysoy Pasta by Bunker</h3><p>说起意大利面的包装设计，你或许对那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/24178.html\">结合金发女郎</a>的概念包装印象深刻。今天要介绍的这套包装是波黑创意工作室 <a href=\"http://www.madeinbunker.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bunker</a> 为意面品牌 Delysoy 制作的，也采用了富有趣味的镂空设计。如果说“金发女郎”是从意面形状上作区分的话，Bunker 的创意则进一步强调了个性：Delysoy 的这些意面恰好是由不同颜色的大豆制成的，设计师们就为每一款意面设计了一个人物造型。除此之外，活泼的配色和漂亮的排版也是让这个包装能够在货架上夺人眼球的关键。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170159DegmPGKCTSYFZqV8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170158MamhS7YVwAxlyHrG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170158Rygu9BdqHL7stEXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170159fYeB17myi6juM8Gq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208170158o4MzDAUYF7RLdwXs.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}